benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: GET /1.0/kb/accounts/block/{blockingId}/auditLogsWithHistory - Retrieve blocking state audit logs with history by id

gaps: Explicit 403 Forbidden scenario for insufficient permissions
Response schema validation across all edge cases (beyond TC19)
Backward compatibility with legacy headers beyond TC15
Concurrent access performance beyond basic concurrency (TC16)
recommendations: Add dedicated pagination tests for large result sets to confirm proper paging behavior and limits.
Add tests validating caching headers (ETag/Cache-Control) and cache validation semantics.
Introduce rate-limiting/throttling tests to ensure proper handling of bursts.
Add scenarios for 403 Forbidden when permissions are insufficient, in addition to 401.
Strengthen schema validation across more edge cases (TC19) and include explicit schema mismatch tests.
Expand backward compatibility tests to cover additional legacy header scenarios beyond TC15.
Enhance performance testing with more extensive concurrency and throughput measurements (beyond TC16).
